    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 9. Ctenus monaghani spec. nov., holotype male from Laos, habitus (5 dorsal; 6 ventral; 7 lateral; 8 prosoma, ventral; 9 coxae III and IV, ventral, showing fields of stout spines)." ;
